The datasets I've explored for capstone project are as following:
  1. The flikr dataset uploaded in this repo: Flicker8k_Dataset and Flickr8k_text 
     This data set is 1 GB in size. 
  2. The flickr30k dataset is the same dataset but larger in size (4GB). The data is available in this link: 
      https://www.kaggle.com/hsankesara/flickr-image-dataset
  3. COCO image dataset: 
      https://cocodataset.org/#download
